<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وأما الركعتان بعد الوتر؛<span class="c5"> فكان يقرأ فيهما:</span> <span class="c3">{إِذَا زُلْزِلَتِ الأَرْضُ}</span> <span class="c2">(٩٩: ٨)</span> ، و <span class="c3">{قُلْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>يَا أَيُّهَا الكَافِرُونَ} . <span class="c2">(١٠٩: ٦)</span> . <span class="c2">(ص ٥٤٤)</span> .<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
